pcePcepExtClientEntry OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX PcePcepClientEntry MAX-ACCESS not-accessible STATUS current DESCRIPTION "An entry in this table represents a PCEP client. An entry can be created by a network administrator or by an SNMP agent as instructed by PCEP."
